    public interface AppContextService<X extends AppContextService<X>>
extends AppContextCleanup
    Interface for Services stored in an AppContext. Though the implementation of the services can form a class hierarchy the target services should not, as each one should be registered under a unique service. Service classes should be tagged with a PreRequisiteService to identify dependencies.
